data.text:
WYNANTSKILL>>The Wynantskill Union Free School District announces the second quarter honor roll of Gardner-Dickinson School.

GRADE 8

High Honor Roll: Jordan Audi, Isabella Casale, Timothy Cooper, Jewel Evans, Serafina French, Danielle Gumlaw, Giavanna Gumlaw, Keara Kelley, Michael LaBelle, Mackenzie LaVoy, Madison LaVoy, Conner McClain, Stephen McClain, Lauren Nicholl, Averi Panichi, Jessica Rebhun, John Roullier, Natalie Stoner, Aidan Sullivan, Kaylie Watts, Shana Winchip.

Honor Roll: Anthony DeGiorgio, Isabella Fanning, Morgan Feehan-Littlejohn, Rachel Fredricks, Raymond Hoffman, Jimi McCarthy, Paige Nicholson.

GRADE 7

High Honor Roll: Christopher Allen, Justin Cioffi, Kaylan Comenole, Ryan Coonan, Katelyn Cooper, Brooklyn Darling, Gracie Driscoll, Brody French, Amaya George, Abbie Hudspath, Rachel Kane, Olivia MacGregor, Courtney Miller, Christina Parrottino, Kia Plumadore, Aidan Tenzyk, Leah Thomas.

Honor Roll: Joseph Catone, Bruce Gumlaw Jr., Nicco Perrotti, Ryan Reardon, Gabriel Rivenburg, Tyler Roy, Austin Winchip.

Originally Published: February 27, 2014 at 10:53 a.m.
